      "role": "user",
      "content": "sometimes i sit in these cafes in cities i dont even know and i realize that if i just didnt show up tomorrow... like, if i literally just ceased to exist... nothing would actually change. no one would even notice the gap i left behind. it feels like i'm just a ghost walking around.",
